      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;-perplexity-launches-50m-vc-fund--because-ai-money-never-sleeps-&#34;&gt;💰 Perplexity Launches $50M VC Fund – Because AI Money Never Sleeps 🤖💸&lt;a href=&#34;#-perplexity-launches-50m-vc-fund--because-ai-money-never-sleeps-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If &lt;strong&gt;raising $500 million&lt;/strong&gt; at a &lt;strong&gt;$9 billion valuation&lt;/strong&gt; wasn’t enough, Perplexity is now &lt;strong&gt;giving away&lt;/strong&gt; some of that cash! 🤑&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;They’re launching a &lt;strong&gt;$50M venture fund&lt;/strong&gt; to invest in &lt;strong&gt;seed and pre-seed startups&lt;/strong&gt;—because &lt;strong&gt;AI search engines aren’t just for searching, they’re also for funding.&lt;/strong&gt; 🔍💸&lt;/p&gt;</description>
